trapped, fire on floor 4 (contained). **Recommendation:** deploy rescue teams; 
stage structural engineer with real-time accelerometer.

✅ **Metro Overpass** — Drone survey confirms spalling on supports 14–17 with 
exposed (uncorroded) rebar; deck deflection within tolerance; adjacent supports 
unaffected. **Risk:** corrosion potential, further spalling if aftershocks 
continue. **Recommendation:** single-lane vehicle traffic safe under flag crew; 
commuter rail remains suspended pending full engineering load-rating analysis.

